{"tid":1870744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1330 大埔天后廟要人!!!!","createTime":"2020-02-09T05:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T08:33:48.000Z","uid":242889,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c0958f097b14d2d147e024ec9ba40cec01fbf2eb","tid":1870744,"uid":242889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1KfZPfp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1KfZPfp.jpg&h=5e609cac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大埔人出嚟未阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個診所喺正市中心 唔好話對面 樓上已經有人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對面又有一間小學加兩間中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對面仲有老人院 餐廳 酒吧 人流咁撚多<br />\n仲要大埔區既學生年年都去嗰到體檢<br />\n如果啲支那帶菌者行嚟行去 後果一定不堪設想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大埔人 一陣1點半 風水廣場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對肺炎診所巡遊  ❗️❗️❗️"},{"pid":"993bcb3afed31ead46db99605838a23fcb90849e","tid":1870744,"uid":242889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:05:17.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 雖一出路（1/10）"},{"pid":"1eaff9ed5495e059c94dbade32f6f1d2c8f5cb1f","tid":1870744,"uid":242889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T05:05:32.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 雖一出路 （2/10)"},{"pid":"02eb426f6135d1c42d6cfe11dab6db759dda4609","tid":1870744,"uid":242889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0